events.name: iOS Dev Scout March Meetup
events.description: Venue: PayPal @Millennia Tower - 14th Floor, 1 Temasek Avenue. Nearby MRT: Promenade Bring your IC as the same will be needed by Millennia Security. Speakers: Takemura Ori, Subhransu Behera, Aizat Omar Agenda: 7:00PM: Game Development with SpriteKit and Swift by Subh 7:30PM: Dinner & Networking 7:45PM: Aizat will talk about how to use Photo library to grab photos from device photo gallery. 8:15PM: Sheep that tells 4D Numbers (That's the only hint Ori gave me)
